   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lent Easter Appeal 2019 Climate Resilience</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The SPD led Lent appeal for 2019 will be code 9 income  for co-funded projects under the Climate resilience theme. So far 4 projects in need of co funding have been agreed in Burkina Faso, Malawi, Nicaragua and Kenya. There will also be additional funds which are yet to be decided where to allocate and so additional income sources will be created in due course. This is a multi income source package.</narrative>
